== Ubuntu Natty Narwhal Release Party 2011 Winterthur ==

=== Date and time ===

The Ubuntu Natty Narwhal Release Party will happen on Saturday the 30th of April 2011 at the ZLI Winterthur, starting from 3.00 PM

Everybody who is interested is invited to take part.

=== Attendance ===

It would be nice if you could <nowiki>[[http://loco.ubuntu.com/events/team/866/detail/|register]]</nowiki> if you are planning to take part, but it's not required.
